code: import axios from'axios';var port=process.env.PORT||3000;var api=axios.create({baseURL:'http://localhost:'+port+'/program'});export var insertGoal=function insertGoal(payload){return api.post("/program",payload);};export var getAllGoals=function getAllGoals(){return api.get("/program");};export var updateGoalById=function updateGoalById(id,payload){return api.put("/program/".concat(id),payload);};export var deleteGoalById=function deleteGoalById(id){return api.delete("/program/".concat(id));};export var getGoalById=function getGoalById(id){return api.get("/program/".concat(id));};var apis={insertGoal:insertGoal,getAllGoals:getAllGoals,updateGoalById:updateGoalById,deleteGoalById:deleteGoalById,getGoalById:getGoalById};export default apis;
